data.title: Marriage Site of Julia Roberts
data.meta_description:
St. James Lutheran Church
	1206 N. Miller Avenue
	Marion, IN
	
	Julia Roberts married Lyle Lovett at this church on June 27th, 1993 while Lovett was on tour. Tim Robbins and Susan Sarandon were also present at the ceremony.
